WEBVTT

00:00.477 --> 00:02.477
<i>So, Here is what you missed on
Glee: Quinn's got a new look,</i>

00:02.545 --> 00:04.096
<i>and a new crowd of Skanks.
Kurt got Blaine to join</i>

00:04.180 --> 00:06.431
<i>the New Directions, which is
good, because Santana got</i>

00:06.516 --> 00:08.517
<i>kicked out, and Sugar Motta wasn't good
enough to get in. Who cares what you think?</i>

00:08.568 --> 00:10.235
<i>McKinley's doing West Side
Story, and Kurt and Rachel</i>

00:10.320 --> 00:11.687
<i>need the leads
so they can get into NYADA.</i>

00:11.738 --> 00:13.155
<i>Sue's using her
run for Congress</i>

00:13.222 --> 00:14.523
<i>to come after the arts.
Believe it or not,</i>

00:14.574 --> 00:15.991
<i>still not
a big fan of the Glee Club.</i>

00:16.058 --> 00:17.693
<i>And that's what you missed
on Glee.</i>

